  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A  platform that provides reliable and authoritive  information about science and technology, and explores how science and technology can reduce poverty, improve health and raise standards of living around the worldR4D is DFID&apos;s Research portal. It provides current and historical information about DFID funded research, along with news, case studies and publicationsR4D is DFID&apos;s Research portal. It provides current and historical information about DFID supported researchTo improve external access to the latest information on research funded by DFID by making available the Research for Development website, database and Open Data.   Research for Development also provides external access to DFID research news and case studies as well as information on DFID funded research going back to 1990To improve external access to the latest information on research funded by DFID by making available the Research for Development website,database and Open Data</narrative>
  </description>
